  "title": "Warehouse Assistant",
  "description": "<p>· Assisting the warehouse manager in providing efficiency and effectiveness of the warehouse operation</p><p>· Manage all logistics activities within the warehouse</p><p>· Assist with the loading and unloading of containers for both import and export operations of containers as required</p><p>· Perform housekeeping and maintenance of tools and equipment</p><p>· Perform any other ad-hoc operational duties as assigned</p><p>· Carry out housekeeping to ensure workplace is safe & tidy</p><p>· Other store duties as and when assigned Requirements</p><p>· Fit for warehouse duty, may need to carry loose items.</p><p>· Maintaining a clean, safe, and organized work area</p><p>· Preferable with Forklift License or experience operating a forklift is an advantage</p><p>. Class 3 Driving License will be an added advantage</p><p>· Willing to do manual work</p><p>. At least 1 Year of experience as Warehouse Assistant</p><p>. Ensure the warehouse is clean, organized, and compliant with safety standards</p><p>. Able to start work immediately is an advantage</p>",
